  "2152460": {
    "name": "Miniland Adventure: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 2152460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/9991e4c85990bff61ae7d141c1524b87.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=614 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/9991e4c85990bff61ae7d141c1524b87.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/9991e4c85990bff61ae7d141c1524b87.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br>《Miniland：序章》仅是对完整版游戏的玩法给予部分演示。<br><br>Miniland 是一款游戏，您可以在其中做任何想做的事！ 当然你还是需要时常吃点东西，但除此之外，没有任何限制！<br><br>你从一小块土地开始，随着时间的推移，你可以用你每天收到的生物群系瓷砖自行扩展。<br><br>很快，你就会发现自己置身于一座又大又漂亮的房子里，此外还有一个农场，制作新工具并探索洞穴。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开创世界</h2><br>每天你都会收到一堆生物群系图块，你可以将其放置在任何你想要的地方！游戏中有多个生物群系，包括：不同的森林、沙漠、草原、雪地、稀树草原、高原等等！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/835e2c9a09b8aa2d079d3ee34eaf5f8c.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/835e2c9a09b8aa2d079d3ee34eaf5f8c.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/835e2c9a09b8aa2d079d3ee34eaf5f8c.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集资源和制作</h2><br>你可以通过砍伐树木、开采金属、掠夺怪物以及制作更多物品来收集大量资源！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/1ca1c60e87f0c6f9e85e544cc6448d5b.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/1ca1c60e87f0c6f9e85e544cc6448d5b.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/1ca1c60e87f0c6f9e85e544cc6448d5b.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >采矿和制作新工具</h2><br>登上地下探索黑暗的洞穴并开采珍贵的材料！更好的材料带来更好的工具：斧头、镐、剑、弹弓、画笔等等！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/f406e1bd3771b86b5c835c7eccc12781.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/f406e1bd3771b86b5c835c7eccc12781.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/f406e1bd3771b86b5c835c7eccc12781.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和装饰</h2><br>使用不同类型的木材来制作地板、墙壁、栅栏和各种装饰品，你可以建造你梦想中的房子和周围环境。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/db235713ffff6f06396d6709aaf37ac5.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/db235713ffff6f06396d6709aaf37ac5.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/db235713ffff6f06396d6709aaf37ac5.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >农业</h2><br>你种过西兰花、芦笋或萝卜吗？也许你在饲养羊驼、鸵鸟或追逐浣熊？不管你有没有<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/d335b54a5ffeb012055036d3dc937a80.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/d335b54a5ffeb012055036d3dc937a80.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/d335b54a5ffeb012055036d3dc937a80.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与怪物战斗</h2><br>黑暗带来了怪物。你能与他们战斗，还是只为你的生命而战？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/4c1a17fbc892e0e16e08bb015596f35f.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/4c1a17fbc892e0e16e08bb015596f35f.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/4c1a17fbc892e0e16e08bb015596f35f.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与地精交易</h2><br>你会在世界各地找到手无寸铁的妖精，你会为他们建造房屋以使用独特的物品进行有利可图的交易吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/a5462193e39bc311b59ebfb82133eb57.poster.avif?t=1717746950\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/a5462193e39bc311b59ebfb82133eb57.webm?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152460/extras/a5462193e39bc311b59ebfb82133eb57.mp4?t=1717746950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
